history.name: WebSurfer
history.content:
OpenCV added support for the Mask-RCNN model in version 4.1.0, released in April 2019. Key contributors for this version included:
1. Alexander Alekhin
2. Dmitry Kurtaev
3. Vadim Pisarevsky
These individuals played significant roles in the integration and development of the Mask-RCNN support within OpenCV.
